# Secrets — NEVER commit. dotenvx keeps values in .env as `encrypted:` ciphertext, but the
# raw files and the private decryption keys must stay local. Globbed so a renamed variant
# (.env.local, .env.production.keys, .signing-key.dev.json) can't slip through. Mirrors
# earlbear-agentic-workflow/.gitignore; the check-env-encrypted hook is the belt to this
# suspenders (it fails a commit if a tracked .env* still holds a plaintext value).
.env
.env.local
.env.keys
.env.*.keys
# ES256 signing key for the Supabase token exchange — private JWK (also matches the symlink
# to the shared gtm key used for the local /api/auth-token mint). NEVER commit.
.signing-key*.json
